name: Chakra Incense Balancing Kit
description: This Chakra Incense Balancing Kit contains 7 individual packs of 10 incense sticks. Each pack represents one of the seven chakras and a different fragrance; Root - Strawberry, Sacral - Orange, Solar Plexus - Lemon, Heart - Mint, Throat - Blueberry, Third Eye - Lavender, Crown - Blackberry. Wooden Incense holder included. Dimensions: H22cm x W27cm x D2cm; Material: Incense
